records.addlTxt:
Sentence is withheld.  Defendant is placed on probation to DOC for three (3) years.
Conditions of probation:
1) Repay $400.00 in buy money to the Metro Drug Unit;
2) Full-time employment or school or combination;
3) Random drug screens and pay for same;
4) If agent finds the Phoenix assessment adequate, no AODA assessment; if not, defendant must undergo another AODA assessment; 
5) COMPAS assessment;
6) Nine (9) months Manitowoc County Jail, under the Huber Law.  Six (6) months served up front commencing 06-14-16 by 5:00 p.m., three (3) months stayed to be imposed at agent's discretion.  Huber is to include child care and schooling release;
7) Pay costs of the action; and
8) Pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC.
Minutes.
